    <item>
      <title>[이별전쟁] ‘月수입 2000만원’ 강사 남편, 나를 ‘사업 노예’로 만들었다</title>
      <link>https://www.chosun.com/national/court_law/2025/01/04/XGAA5MPJWRG2ZOROUUW23FDKBQ/</link>
      <guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.chosun.com/national/court_law/2025/01/04/XGAA5MPJWRG2ZOROUUW23FDKBQ/</guid>
      <dc:creator>법무법인 시작</dc:creator>
      <description/>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 20:30:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <content:encoded>&lt;b&gt;편집자주: 이 기사는 이혼 소송 과정에서 필요한 법률 지식을 제공할 목적으로 제작됐습니다. 기사 내용은 실제 사례를 각색했습니다. 기사 내 언급되는 이름과 지명 등이 실제와 같은 경우가 있더라도 이는 우연에 의한 것임을 밝힙니다.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;격주 토요일·일요일 연재.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/IFW7MBU25JATFO66WAPVACULCA.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/DNCWVG3BZRBRRIDMLNH5XOQWQY.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/WLYHS45UPBCCBMVYL6KHZTP7HU.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/QA7GEJ3DHNDCZAHMUKMQBEFCVA.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/KDEJ4ILZGBBC5DCMKUJTM43F3E.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;figure&gt;&lt;img align="center" src="https://cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/chosun/6MXF6BYMWZFVLALCP7RMGCBHOU.jpg"&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;small&gt;&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[이별전쟁] 수학과 결혼했어요②에서 계속&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;&amp;lt;다른 회차 보기&amp;gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[이별전쟁 15-1] 네버앤딩스토리&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="https://m.site.naver.com/1zgpy"&gt;https://m.site.naver.com/1zgpy&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;[이별전쟁 15-2]&lt;br&gt;&l